snippet.title: Nick Toon Twister 3-D - Intro/Opening Cutscene
snippet.description:
An intro to the rare game I used to play when I was a kid that is inspired by Microsoft 3D Movie Maker featuring Characters from your favorite Nick shows you've remebered back then like Spongebob, Fairly Oddparents, Jimmy Neutron and Rugrats, but Kimi (from Rugrats) had a cameo appearance as the CD-Rom disc cover/label.
It was released for Scholastic in 2003.

I've made several cartoons made of Toon Twister 3-D like "Carzillo", so you can watch these on my channel If you want to see.
